Package: spectr
Type: Package
Title: Calculate the periodogram of a time-course
Version: 0.0.0.9015
Authors@R: as.person(c(
  "Jake Hughey <jakejhughey@gmail.com> [aut, cre]",
  "Michael Tackenberg <m.tackenberg@gmail.com> [aut]"))
Description: Provides a consistent interface to use various methods to calculate
  the periodogram and estimate the period of a rhythmic time-course. Methods
  include Lomb-Scargle, fast Fourier transform, and three versions of the
  chi-square periodogram.
URL: https://github.com/hugheylab/spectr
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
Imports:
  data.table (>= 1.12.2),
  foreach (>= 1.5.0),
  imputeTS (>= 3.0),
  lomb (>= 1.2)
Suggests:
  knitr,
  rmarkdown,
  testthat (>= 2.3.2)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
